title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: The rows of the field arrest abruptly at the edge of this small patch of dirt, the soil here left untouched and unturned.  Sprigs of grass and weeds stand out here and there against the dark hue of the earth, their colors vibrant like those of the surrounding tents and booths.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, southeast, south, west, northwest
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
